text: This is not me saying that Russian players or anybody does not have the right to be upset over this because they do, but I'm just saying we should recognize that you can't just expect people to drop their values, even if it means some people won't get to play the pack

author: Ethan Harris
text: I know if I personally were in a situation like that I wouldn't want to compromise my morals either. The Sims team are all people who have their own values and I think that type of integrity and dedication should be commended.
